title: Lulz: A Corruption of LOL soundtrack
description:
A soundtrack for Anonymous, by Anonymous, with all the memetic songs to date.

This soundtrack was started by an Anon who /r/ help from 420chan&#039;s /m/, which allows music uploads.  Over a few weeks they compiled this album.  ID3 tags of the songs contain basic information on why they were included, though if you didn&#039;t know, you should lurk moar.

Disk I - Pure Memetics (all the classic meme songs, current and old)
1. Will Smith - The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air (2:57)
2. Rick Astley - Never Gonna Give You Up (3:35)
3. Tay Zonday - Chocolate Rain (4:52)
4. Andrew W. K. - Party Hard (3:04)
5. GLaDOS - Still Alive (2:56)
6. DarkMateria - The Picard Song (4:40)
7. 403 - Southern Cross (3:42)
8. Lazy Town - You Are A Pirate (1:52)
9. Trans-Siberian Orchestra - 1812 Overture (4:07)
10. Oingo Boingo - Little Girls (3:43)
11. Was (Not Was) - Everybody Walk the Dinosaur (4:22)
12. DragonForce - Through the Fire and Flames (7:24)
13. CODA Remix: Shii&#039;s Song - Longcat&#039;s Song (2:10)
14. Bobby &#039;Boris&#039; Pickett - Monster Mash (3:09)
15. Anonymous - 7chan Theme Song (5:54)

Disk II - Corruption (remixes of memes and mashups)
1. DJ AnounymOS - so i herd u liek musics (oh lawd, is dat sum insurgency) version 2.1 (6:47)
2. DJ Gotcha - Over 9000 (Remix) (1:07)
3. manish - Series of Tubes (Net Neutrality Dance Mix) (2:08)
4. PoleJR @ PinkGator - Chocolate Rain : An Original Remix by PoleJR (6:08)
5. DJ Jazzy Jeff & Fresh Prince - Yo Home To Bel-Air (3:24)
6. Metronomy w/ dj AnonPBear - You could easily have me [Internet Hate Machine] (3:08)
7. Funtastic Power! - 300 This is Sparta (EXTENDED fun times mix) (2:15)
8. Steve Ballmer - Developers (3:01)
9. Tay Zonday FEAT Mista Johnson - Cherry Chocolate Rain (2:49)
10. Anonymous - Internet Haet Machine (1:17)
11. REDALiCE - Lucky Star REDALiCE Remix (5:03)
12. Morbicae - I&#039;ma Firin&#039; Mah Lazor (2:47)
13. Anonymous - Flight of Tacgnol (3:32)

Disk III - /f/b/i/ (various tracks from famous flash videos and background music from /b/ and /i/nvasions.)
1. DMX - Where The Hood At? (4:52)
2. Infected Mushroom - Becoming Insane (Radio Mix) (3:12)
3. Funta - Kao Dekai (3:23)
4. Another Bad Creation - Playground Castlevania Remix (3:54)
5. DJ Sharpnel - Pantsoo (5:58)
6. Infected Mushroom - I Wish (Skazi Remix) (8:01)
7. Loituma - Ievas Polka (original acapella) (2:46)
8. Konami Kukeiha Club - LONGCAT flash (Burnin Heat DDR) (1:33)
9. Rednex - Cotton Eye Joe (2:54)
10. Witches - There She Is !!! (3:23)
11. Unknown - Supergirl (Waha mix) (0:43)
12. The Red Army Choir - National Anthem of the USSR (3:44)
